high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Cut the potato place next to the sink into slices.
Turn left and go to the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave door, put the knife in the microwave and close the door.
Turn right and go back to the potato slices on the counter.
Pick up one potato slice from the counter.
Turn left and go back to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the potato slice in and cook for 5 minutes. Open the door and take out the potato slice.
Turn right and go to the black table on your left.
Put the potato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato slice and put it on a black table.

high_descs: go to the counter to the right of the fridge

take the knife to the counter to the left of the sink
cut the potato on the counter
take the knife to the microwave
put the knife in the microwave
go back to the counter with the sliced potato
pick up the end of the potato
take the potato to the microwave
put the potato in the microwave then remove
take the cooked potato slice to the dining table
set the slice on the table
anns.task_desc: put a knife and a potato slice in the microwave before putting the potato on the table

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter between the fridge and the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Cut the potato on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left and head to the microwave above the stove.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn left and go back to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn around, go across the room and turn left toward the black table.
Put the slice of potato on the table to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on the black table.
